{"tid":1775080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要單以良知自居，要以勝利為目標","createTime":"2019-12-08T15:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:34:45.000Z","uid":93141,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"b85a8f6d9a1076e5ecf1e6b67d84fca8902f6083","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"要明白攬炒既意思<br />\n攬炒係令事不關己既人逼住要一齊反抗，包括市民，包括商家，包括公務員，包括法庭<br />\n係架，好撚自私架，但攬炒本身就係不顧少數人利益架啦，係好撚自私架<br />\n<br />\n有好多人鍾意講咩藍黃是政見，黑白是良知<br />\n其實對家都一樣係保護緊自己既私有財產，一樣係人權<br />\n我從來都唔會以良知自居，兩邊各有各既正義，對我黎講我地就係正義，黃就係正義，藍就係邪惡，共產黨就係邪惡，只有勝利者先配講之後既道德同良知<br />\n<br />\n當提出反共同獨立時，就話冇武器，冇軍火點革命。<br />\n到有人真係有嘅時候，又話係對家做戲。<br />\n話就話核彈都唔割，而家有支手槍放個火，有好多人已經割晒蓆，咁點算好？<br />\n<br />\n好多人之前反對我地唔係因為我地既做法有咩問題，而係佢地覺得贏唔到，好多人係買馬心態，與其譴責強者不如譴責弱者實冇錯。<br />\n點解我地會越來越多同路人？唔止因為佢地支持我地理念同反對對方做法，而係我地一次次成功，越來越接近勝利。612如是，71如是，理大如是，今次火燒法院亦如是。<br />\n<br />\n所以最有效爭取民意既方法唔單係動之以情說之以理，而係堅持做你認為係正義既一件事，做到好，做到贏，做到有勝利既曙光，咁就有最多民意。<br />\n<br />\n好多勇武既手足無論放火，裝修定打狗，就係堅持緊佢地既正義，用一次次既成功為我地爭取民意。<br />\n<br />\n所以諗割席，叫佢地停手之前，停一停，諗一諗，點先係最有效既勝利方法？<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位勇敢既手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反擊</span></span><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"f3cdc5200afcd1ecda97a333293607d1bdaa2651","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2516cae5c316ecf9e2113ef5abb30f699358ae","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fe57e889ca9df759c1c750a745b01088da4815","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c263d20f698b73639b55f280209ff30bb3fad3cf","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23209ead364477cceea412b197892f037ec723f","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fea130c8c41dfff5f74a80605bbd9842a4dbf47","tid":1775080,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0a993f492e8f41d4285671e12d012a4a5fcf6387","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4f707da1754c28abd1779da8fb378b366e3a16","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fea130c8c41dfff5f74a80605bbd9842a4dbf47","tid":1775080,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1250360ddc9cb048d50f09963e1944cc2f842f","tid":1775080,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"396ef10b58ade27a5a10df7ec4b48ba9a7778c11","tid":1775080,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"冇人睇？"},{"pid":"106ee92d053e501eb14ad618559863916ef57b29","tid":1775080,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"396ef10b58ade27a5a10df7ec4b48ba9a7778c11","tid":1775080,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"冇人睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1543deaa63f6a